      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a good start for the outline. Can you expand on the \"modern civilization\" part? Like, when we talk about these modern structures, are we mostly looking at the development of nation-states and industrialization in Europe and North America? I want to make sure my paper captures why that specific path is seen as the standard for \"civilization.\"",
